{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_DripBlood}}
'''A_DripBlood'''<br />
(no parameters)

Spawns a {{Class|Blood}} actor within eight map units of the calling actor on both horizontal axes, gives it a random horizontal velocity between -4 and +4 on the same axes, and sets its gravity property to 0.125.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|RedAxe}} and derived classes.

